data.description: This two bedroom one bathroom Home sits on a corner lot right around the corner from the Sierra Del Rio Golf Course & the entrance to Elephant Butte State Park. The Home has a fenced in covered carport. The newer roof was installed in 2021, twelve solar panels installed in 2022 & four double pained windows installed in 2011. Other improvements are footing & foundation installed in 2011, R-30 ceiling 2022, new shower controls 2023 and drywall & texture 2023. This is the perfect get away Home for fishing, golfing, hiking or just having fun at the lake.
